    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Camden</name>
                    <date when="1888-07-25">Wednesday PM July 25 '88<ptr target="loc.07647_n1"
                        /></date>
                </dateline>  
                <salute/>
            </opener>

            <p>Weather perfect continued&#8212;they say yesterday was fearfully hot, but I didn't
                mind it&#8212;the hours rather dull but ab't as usual &#38; no setback. <hi
                    rend="italic">Nov</hi>: <hi rend="italic">Boughs</hi><ptr target="n3999"/> copy done&#8212;the three letters from 
                Rhys,<ptr target="n4152"/> Miss Bates,<ptr target="n4171"/> &#38; our old Japanee friend<ptr target="n4980"/>
                I will enclose<ptr target="loc.07647_n2"/>&#8212;(don't want them back)&#8212;</p>

            <p>If any gaps of the proof pages up to 104 exist, mention it &#38; I will
                remit&#8212;Keep my room yet&#8212;am sitting now (&#38; in four fifths time day) in
                the capacious ratan-seated arm chair&#8212;my condition of feebleness &#38;
                locomotive capacity is fearful&#8212;the brain works ab't as before&#8212;&#38;
                muscle &#38; grip of arms (especially right) strong &#38; glib perhaps as
                ever&#8212;</p>

            <closer>
                <salute/>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
    </text>
